de.must.print
Class PrintableCallback

java.lang.Object
  de.must.print.PrintableCallback
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrintableAttribute, PrintableColumn
public class PrintableCallback
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrintableColumn

A component to print text which may be assembled by the calling class via callback. Thus, special and combined values may be constructed while standard stuff is handled easily by PrintableText and so on.
